        "rich_text_8DL9Df": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Introduction",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Every love story has its chapters - from shy beginnings to sharing secrets to whispering promises of a much awaited forever. Jewelry is that tangible form of love symbolising an emotion too deep to be expressed in words. Among the many milestones, promise rings and proposal rings are special. They’re both significant yet very distinct in the meanings they each carry. </p><p>This guide covers everything you need to know about the two - meaning, symbolism, and emotional depth each of them carry, helping you understand which one fits your beautiful love story better.</p>",
            "custom_id": "introduction",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bUfHBT": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Evolution of Romantic Jewelry ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>The Evolution of Romantic Jewelry </h2><p>The tradition of exchanging rings dates back thousands of years. Back then, in Egypt, a circular band signified eternal love - the one that has no beginning and no end. The Romans formalized this practice of betrothal rings, made out of precious metals such as gold to define the permanence of a married life. Over time, this practice has become more than just the formalized ritual in a marriage. It is not just a solitaire diamond engagement ring and a wedding band. It is going beyond that, expressing gratitude and love.</p>",
            "custom_id": "the-evolution",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_BJTXhY": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/The_Evolution_Of_Romantic_Jewelry.jpg",
            "text": "<p>By the 16th century, promise rings were seen in Europe with poetry and affectionate words engraved on the rings, then called ‘posy rings’. These were not merely custom <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-ring\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"engagement rings\">engagement rings</a>, but a thoughtful gift of announcing that a forever together is just one step away. Today, these traditions are made even more beautiful with proposal rings gifted in the most memorable way, with stories of the promise ring, and then the proposal ring forever etched on the hearts of the couple. </p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "0-52ct-emerald-oval-round-shape-diamond-toi-et-moi-ring",
              "solitaire-round-shape-diamond-engagement-ring-1-30-cts"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_3i3W7r": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "What Is A Promise Ring ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>What Is A Promise Ring </h2><p>A promise ring, also called a pre-engagement ring, is a heartfelt gesture symbolizing commitment. It signifies loyalty and promises a life together. A friendship ring or a promise ring is gifted to a romantic partner, as a way to express that they are sure of living their life ahead together, no matter the hardships. </p>",
            "custom_id": "what-is",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_XNbEab": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/What_Is_A_Promise_Ring_2fc8e456-b325-4e21-9135-24970208d632.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Modern couples use promise rings to express a myriad of thoughts: </p><p><em>I am committed to you. </em></p><p><em>We have a future together. </em></p><p><em>We will be reunited soon, free from the chaos and the distance. </em></p><p><em>My love stays constant, and I’d do anything to be with you for the rest of my life. </em></p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "0-12ct-round-diamond-channel-eternity-band",
              "0-21ct-half-eternity-diamond-band"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_dn6kJd": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "What Is A Promise Ring  Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Some exchange them before engagement rings for women, and some gift them during anniversaries. While the time of marriage may not be nailed down, a promise ring signifies a partner’s willingness to someday want to start a family together. It is one of the most romantic gifts that a partner could gift to their other half. Just like custom engagement rings, you can also customize matching promise rings to wear daily as a reminder of the love you share and the good days coming ahead.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_iyjamA": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "What Does A Promise Ring Look Like?",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>What Does A Promise Ring Look Like?</h2><p>Promise rings are often delicate and minimalistic. They carry a softness in their tone with fine bands topped with infinity, hearts, or knots to symbolize love. A promise ring becomes even more special with a customized engraving on the inner or outer side of the band. They’re designed for daily wear, elegant yet understated. A promise ring is made to cherish the sweet beginnings of love that promises to be together forever. </p>",
            "custom_id": "what-does-a",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Jc4E4r": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "What Is A Proposal Ring ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>What Is A Proposal Ring </h2>",
            "custom_id": "what-is",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_cxVKj9": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/What_Is_A_Proposal_Ring.jpg",
            "text": "<p>A proposal ring, often called an engagement ring, is the most iconic symbol of commitment. The word ‘proposal’ is often related to an event of asking - Will you marry me? On agreeing with the intention, essentially the screaming of a “YES”, a proposal ring is slipped on to mark this moment of a promise fulfilled. The best <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-ring\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"engagement rings \">engagement rings </a>reflect the relationship shared, symbolizing love made out of precious metals such as gold or platinum that stay with you forever.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "4-prong-princess-cut-solitaire-ring",
              "2-11-ct-princess-cut-solitaire-engagement-ring",
              "mens-solitaire-princess-diamond-band",
              "mens-channel-set-princess-cut-ring"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_adKm8W": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "What Is A Proposal Ring  Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>A tiny detail to note is that this proposal ring can be temporary, while an engagement ring can be later picked out by the couple together for the engagement ceremony. </p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_xAGLJV": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "What Does A Proposal Ring Look Like",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>What Does A Proposal Ring Look Like</h2><p>Proposal rings are designed to dazzle. The grander, the better! They feature a center diamond, symbolizing unity and eternity. You can choose from various designs such as <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/solitaire-rings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"solitaire rings\">solitaire rings</a> - the most classic and timeless, halo rings - a circle of diamonds enhancing brilliance, three stone rings - the most beloved as they signify the past, the present and the future, all spent with that ‘one’ person. </p>",
            "custom_id": "what-does",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_6WCWXy": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Promise Ring vs Proposal Ring: The Key Differences",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Promise Ring vs Proposal Ring: The Key Differences</h2><p>Though both promise ring and proposal ring carry deep, significant meanings in a relationship, they both carry distinct meanings and are different in many ways. For your convenience, we made a simple table for you to know the difference at one glimpse! </p>",
            "custom_id": "promise-ring-vs",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_CTP944": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Why These Rings Matter In Your Relationship ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Why These Rings Matter In Your Relationship </h2><p>In an age of instant everything, rings bring back something sacred by expressing intention and the willingness of something permanent. They remind couples that this isn’t a race to walk down the aisle, but a journey. Chocolates melt, flowers wither, and cards tear with time but a ring stays. In a relationship, it is important that words are matched with actions, and these rings do just that! These rings hold your promises and emotions, wrapped around your finger like a constant companion. From a psychological perspective, both a promise ring and a proposal ring act as anchors in the relationship, making the couple deeply emotionally invested in each other. They both signify the kind of love that ages like fine wine, the kind of love that only deepens with time.</p>",
            "custom_id": "why-these-rings",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_9YdFx4": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "When to Give a Promise Ring vs a Proposal Ring",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>When to Give a Promise Ring vs a Proposal Ring</h2><p>The right ring is never about the price, it is about the purpose. </p><p>Ask yourself:</p><ul><li>What does this relationship mean right now?</li><li>What are we ready to commit to?</li><li>What emotion do I want this ring to hold every time it’s seen or worn?</li></ul><p>If your love is growing and evolving while marriage doesn’t seem likely in the near future, then mark this chapter beautifully with a promise ring. It is a quiet reminder that love is not to be rushed, all you need is togetherness through the highs and the lows. If your hearts have already found the rhythm and you are ready for a lifelong commitment, then a proposal ring is due! </p>",
            "custom_id": "when-to-give",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_kiLweW": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Conclusion ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Conclusion </h2><p>At <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lucira Jewelry\">Lucira Jewelry</a>, we believe that every relationship has its own rhythm and every chapter is worth celebrating! Our rings are not just designed to adorn the hand, but to mark a defining moment. Whether it’s the quiet comfort of a promise or the luminous declaration of a proposal, each ring captures a moment that matters. Each Lucira Jewelry piece is crafted to capture these stories of love and warmth.</p>",
            "custom_id": "conclusion",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        }
      },
